    "gp_section_597881648625681340": {
      "type": "gp-section-597881648625681340",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "968b496b4c4528653a2e8abe15e8a577108c23d36db444e842f9f677ec319688_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggGkzemG1js_text": "<span style=\"color:#055BDC;\"><strong>Your Spine Is LITERALLY Suffocating</strong></span>",
        "ggWQIG9fsLw_text": "If You Want To End Neck Pain… You Must Fix Your Dried-Out Discs",
        "ggN5O792d2I_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggN5O792d2I_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggN5O792d2I_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/9f05a511678f4366b8dbd08b1063e83e.mp4",
        "ggymlr3ksYA_text": "If You Want To End Neck Pain… You Must Fix Your Dried-Out Discs",
        "ggj3LHKR5Jp_text": "<p>Here’s what’s really happening in your neck:</p>",
        "gg4YoJ0BCta_text": "<p>Your cervical discs are like jelly donuts between your vertebrae. When they’re hydrated, you move without pain.</p>",
        "ggQAm8x-ujQ_text": "<p>But after age 30, they lose moisture and flatten. Your vertebrae compress together. Nerves get pinched. Muscles spasm trying to protect your spine.</p>",
        "ggRTR9XYKM9_text": "<p>This creates:</p>",
        "ggVM2rptFdA_text": "<p><strong>Constant neck pain and stiffness</strong></p>",
        "ggA8gdNg1BQ_text": "<p><strong>Burning sensations down your arms</strong></p>",
        "ggjny4TEtrb_text": "<p><strong>Headaches and brain fog</strong></p>",
        "ggiOK05sJIZ_text": "<p><strong>That growing hump at your neck base</strong></p>",
        "ggiwIrcyC9Q_text": "<p><strong>Forward head posture that worsens daily</strong></p>",
        "ggWaLe4w3DQ_text": "<p>The problem?</p>",
        "ggGxVIgVHqv_text": "<p>Stretches don’t rehydrate discs. Pills just mask pain. Even surgery can’t restore disc hydration.</p>",
        "gg0045cZav__text": "<p>Until you decompress those vertebrae and rehydrate those discs, the pain always returns.</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_597881648625353660": {
      "type": "gp-section-597881648625353660",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "7f19e1778044758c99c9fe27faeb57a293a4462f1dfadaae35e80f8b2c61bb95_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggzRfc3KmKh_text": "The SmoothSpine Triple Fusion Solution ",
        "gg4GNxuDqa0_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "gg4GNxuDqa0_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "gg4GNxuDqa0_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/0bd4525a8ed9477c9b5bebc4ab6e267b.mp4",
        "ggclZmxOds__text": "The SmoothSpine Triple Fusion Solution ",
        "gg5gEyQLqLG_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine Triple Fusion Neck Massager is the only device that attacks all three root causes simultaneously:</p>",
        "ggu6Yd3u6Yx_text": "<p><strong>1. SPINAL TRACTION THERAPY: </strong>Gently creates space between compressed vertebrae – the same principle used in $30,000 clinical decompression tables. This space allows discs to expand and pull in fluid.</p>",
        "ggyZ6Gf5lWo_text": "<p><strong>2. THERAPEUTIC HEAT: </strong>Increases blood flow by 300%, flooding the area with oxygen and nutrients. Heat also makes disc tissue more permeable for faster rehydration.</p>",
        "ggrYT7cGWvp_text": "<p><strong>3. VIBRATION MASSAGE: </strong>Releases muscle spasms and increases circulation. The oscillation literally helps “pump” fluid back into dehydrated discs.</p>",
        "gglNkdnoYHM_text": "<p>Used together for 15 minutes = Complete disc rehabilitation</p>"
      }
    },
