        "ggb3x-tTKfi_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/f5fba972a4fe45708491f4de304d9373.mp4",
        "ggNDYVqN7Gc_text": "See How It Works In Real Time ",
        "ggFoLsfJU5j_text": "<p>The moment you turn it on: </p>",
        "gg_-MJSPsBq_text": "<p><strong>0–30 Seconds: </strong>Feel immediate decompression as vertebrae gently separate. That crushing pressure on your nerves? Gone.</p>",
        "ggP9YY587P1_text": "<p><strong>30 Seconds–5 Minutes: </strong>Heat floods the area with nutrient-rich blood while traction maintains crucial disc space. You feel muscles finally releasing their death grip.</p>",
        "ggiF75sp5pb_text": "<p><strong>5–10 Minutes: </strong>The combination of sustained traction + heat + vibration creates the perfect environment for disc rehydration. Years of compression begins reversing.</p>",
        "gg7gfYbpkbD_text": "<p><strong>10–15 Minutes: </strong>Your neck naturally returns to proper alignment. The tissue creating that hump softens and begins to reduce.</p>",
        "ggP5xbHg6z-_text": "<p><strong>After 15 minutes: </strong>Turn your head freely. Look down without pain. Stand taller.</p>",
        "ggADn2FzsbO_text": "<p><strong>After 30 days: </strong>Visible posture improvement. Significant hump reduction. Pain-free movement.</p>"
      }
    },
