        "ggBJa8Yn5GB_text": "Frequently Asked Questions",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_0": "<p><strong>How is this different from a regular heating pad?</strong></p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_1": "<p><strong>Will this work for my dowager's hump?</strong></p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_2": "<p><strong>How long before I feel results?</strong></p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_3": "<p><strong>Is it safe for older users?</strong></p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_4": "<p><strong>How often should I use it?</strong></p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_5": "<p><strong>What if it doesn't work for me?</strong></p>",
        "ggJ59b-ywE__text": "<p>Heating pads only provide surface heat. The Triple Fusion combines medical-grade traction (creates space between vertebrae), therapeutic heat (increases blood flow 300%), and vibration massage (releases muscle tension) - all working together to actually rehydrate your discs.</p>",
        "ggOF78_pLax_text": "<p>Yes. The forward head posture and hump are caused by compressed discs and muscle imbalance. By decompressing the spine and releasing tension, most users see visible improvement in 6-8 weeks.</p>",
        "ggGBgdMGN1b_text": "<p>Most users feel immediate relief from the decompression (within 30 seconds). Significant pain reduction typically occurs within 7 days. Posture and hump improvement becomes visible after 4-6 weeks of daily use.</p>",
        "gg5779-Q2LD_text": "<p>Yes. The device uses gentle, controlled traction - much safer than manual adjustments. We have thousands of users in their 60s, 70s, and 80s. Always consult your doctor if you have specific medical conditions.</p>",
        "ggrcqOh_tmz_text": "<p>For best results, use 15 minutes once or twice daily. Most users do one session in the morning and one in the evening.</p>",
        "ggZ3I5t3Bhg_text": "<p>You're covered by our 90-day guarantee. If you don't see results, we'll refund 100% of your purchase. No risk to you.</p>"
      }
    },
